<b>COMMON-----------------------------------------</b>
Ctrl+b                   Prefix
Ctrl+b c                 Create New Window
Ctrl+b d                 Detach Session
Ctrl+b r                 Redraw Interface
Ctrl+b s                 Select Session List
Ctrl+b z                 Maximize Pane
<b>SPLIT------------------------------------------</b>
Ctrl+b "                 Split Horizontal
Ctrl+b %                 Split Vertical
<b>SWAP-------------------------------------------</b>
Ctrl+b {                 Swap Next Pane
Ctrl+b }                 Swap Prev. Pane
<b>RENAME-----------------------------------------</b>
Ctrl+b $                 Rename Session
Ctrl+b ,                 Rename Window
<b>SELECT WINDOW----------------------------------</b>
Ctrl+b n                 Next Window
Ctrl+b p                 Prev. Window
<b>COPY/PASTE BUFFER------------------------------</b>
Ctrl+b [                 Enter Copy Mode
Space                    Visual Block
Ctrl+b ]                 Paste from Buffer
<b>RESURECTION------------------------------------</b>
Ctrl+b Ctrl+s            Save Session
Ctrl+b Ctrl+r            Reload Session
